description: The administration is urging Israel to improve the humanitarian situation in Gaza or risk a cut to arms sales, the starkest threat by the U.S. since the war began last year.
title: Biden Administration Issues Warning to Israel on Gaza Aid

description: Talks over mining company Chemaf in Congo are part of a push by the Biden administration to secure global supplies of a metal used in everything from jet fighters and drones to electric-vehicle batteries.
title: How the U.S. Is Trying to Challenge China's Cobalt Chokehold

description: Many Palestinians are staying put as Israel’s military orders civilians to leave large parts of northern Gaza as it conducts an offensive against Hamas militants.
title: Exhausted Gazans Defy Evacuation Orders as Israel Presses New Offensive
